'''Fantagio'''（{{lang-ko|''' 판타지오'''}}）是一家韓國綜合娛樂公司，事業領域包括藝人企劃、唱片製作、海外公演、電影及電視劇製作等。

2008年由韓國 [[Sidus_HQ|Sidus HQ]] 投資成立，原稱「NOA娛樂」（Network Of Asia），後來於2011年更名為「Fantagio」，是結合「Fantasy」、「Origin」的意思<ref>{{cite news|title=N.O.A Entertainment changes their company name to "Fantagio"|url=https://www.allkpop.com/article/2011/06/n-o-a-entertainment-changes-their-company-name-to-fantagio|publisher=allkpop|date=2011-07-01|language=en|accessdate=2018-02-21|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201131318/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2011/06/n-o-a-entertainment-changes-their-company-name-to-fantagio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年12月28日，創辦人羅丙俊被持有50.07%股份的最大股東－中國金誠集團單方面辭退，執行中方代表理事單獨管理體制。<ref>{{cite news|title=邕聖祐談被中方辭退的 Fantagio 羅丙俊代表：像爸爸一樣的存在|url=https://www.kpopn.com/2018/01/09/%E9%82%95%E8%81%96%E7%A5%90%E8%AB%87%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E8%BE%AD%E9%80%80%E7%9A%84-fantagio-%E7%BE%85%E4%B8%99%E4%BF%8A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%83%8F%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8/|publisher=kpopn|date=2018-01-19|access-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316152724/https://www.kpopn.com/2018/01/09/%E9%82%95%E8%81%96%E7%A5%90%E8%AB%87%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E8%BE%AD%E9%80%80%E7%9A%84-fantagio-%E7%BE%85%E4%B8%99%E4%BF%8A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%83%8F%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8/|archive-date=2018-03-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=邕聖祐談被中方辭退的 Fantagio 羅丙俊代表：像爸爸一樣的存在Fantagio 代表解職事件延燒，傳帶頭抗爭職員遭中方報復停職|url=https://www.kpopn.com/2018/01/26/fantagio-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%82%B3%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7/|publisher=kpopn|date=2018-01-26|access-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316152721/https://www.kpopn.com/2018/01/26/fantagio-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%82%B3%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7/|archive-date=2018-03-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Former Fantagio CEO Na Byung Joon resigns from the company|url=https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/01/former-fantagio-ceo-na-byung-joon-resigns-from-the-company|publisher=allkpop|date=2018-01-27|language=en|accessdate=2018-03-16|archive-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316110601/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/01/former-fantagio-ceo-na-byung-joon-resigns-from-the-company|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年1月25日，羅丙俊宣佈正式請辭。3月16日，羅丙俊公佈成立STARDIUM經紀公司。<ref>{{cite news|title=前 Fantagio 代表羅丙俊成立新公司 STARDIUM 重新出發|url=https://www.kpopn.com/2018/03/16/%E5%89%8D-fantagio-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%BE%85%E4%B8%99%E4%BF%8A%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-stardium-%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC/|publisher=kpopn|date=2011-07-01|language=ko|accessdate=2018-03-16|archive-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316152254/https://www.kpopn.com/2018/03/16/%E5%89%8D-fantagio-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%BE%85%E4%B8%99%E4%BF%8A%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-stardium-%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Former Fantagio CEO Na Byung Joon announces the launch of a new label, STARDIUM|url=https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/03/former-fantagio-ceo-na-byung-joon-announces-the-launch-of-a-new-label-stardium|publisher=allkpop|date=2018-03-16|language=en|accessdate=2018-03-16|archive-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316081727/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/03/former-fantagio-ceo-na-byung-joon-announces-the-launch-of-a-new-label-stardium|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年4月，L&A Holdings從Fantagio的中國籍最大股東Gold Finance Korea(金誠集團子公司)手中收購股份，成為Fantagio的最大股東。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fantagio Gives Update On Legal Dispute And Shares Future Plans|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1424645wpp/fantagio-gives-update-on-legal-dispute-and-shares-future-plans|accessdate=2020-12-14|date=1599682658|work=Soompi|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928232140/https://www.soompi.com/article/1424645wpp/fantagio-gives-update-on-legal-dispute-and-shares-future-plans|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=經紀公司 Fantagio 經營權訴訟結束，最終協議共同經營|url=https://www.kpopn.com/2020/09/10/fantagio-management-right-lawsuit-settle-will-manage-by-both-side|accessdate=2020-12-14|date=2020-09-10|last=Jessica|work=www.kpopn.com|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920222047/https://www.kpopn.com/2020/09/10/fantagio-management-right-lawsuit-settle-will-manage-by-both-side|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年9月，總公司搬到[[SM娛樂|SM娛樂]]第二座舊大樓。

